" </div>",
" <div class=\"graphic\">",
"  <div class=\"figure\" style=\"width: 534px\">",
"   <div class=\"ttl\">",
"    Creation of esophagojejunostomy",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"cntnt\" style=\"width: 514px; height: 716px; background-image: url(data:image/jpeg;base64,);\">",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"lgnd\">",
"    To create the esophagojejunostomy, the anvil of a number 25 end-to-end anastomosis (EEA) stapling device is secured in the distal esophagus and a retrocolic Roux-en-Y esophagojejunostomy is fashioned through the transverse mesocolon using a jejunal limb approximately 40 cm from the Ligament of Treitz.",
